onActionAddPart(ActionEvent) - Method in class controller.AddProductController
ADD SELECTED PART METHOD
This method saves a part selected from the available parts table which is populated from the Inventory allParts list to the Inventory selectedParts list.
onActionAddPart(ActionEvent) - Method in class controller.ModifyProductController
ADD SELECTED PART METHOD
Reads available part table and gets selected part
Adds selected part to associatedParts list for Product Object
If no part is selected an error message is displayed
Because this is an existing object all parts selected by the user to associate to the product are added directly to the associatedParts list
